column2: WARTA KERAJAAN DAERAH MENGUNDI, PUSAT MENGUNDIDAN WAKTU MENGUNDI NEGERI-NEGERI TANAH MELAYU,SABAH DAN SARAWAK 2013

Users to exercise discretion when using the dataset. While every effort has been undertaken to ensure the accuracy, we are not responsible for errors and omission that are arising from the dataset. The new Daerah Mengundi Tanjong Aru appeared in 2016 gazetted but boundaries are not determined.  There was no credible map reference for Daerah Mengundi for Labuan. The location of Daerah Mengundi was only verified with Government Gazette (showing polling stations) and Google Maps.
